---
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-20">
      <p class="reveal text-xs font-semibold text-brand-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 font-display">The Opportunity</p>
      <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1 text-3xl md:text-[2.75rem] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal leading-tight font-display">
        Join the field services evolution
      </h2>
      <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2 mt-5 text-lg text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
        Managing multiple agency relationships across several services and geographies is complex. There's a better way to drive performance, visibility, and collaboration.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8 items-stretch">
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 group relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 hover:border-brand-200/60 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-brand-50">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-8 w-12 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-400 to-brand-300 rounded-b-full"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3 font-display">Increased customer engagement &amp; visit capacity</h3>
        <p class="text-charcoal-light text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          Up to 50% greater customer engagement through our revolutionary allocation model, backed by unrivalled visit capacity across our panel of leading UK field agencies — optimised to postcode level, for every service.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 group relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 hover:border-brand-200/60 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-brand-50">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-8 w-12 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-400 to-brand-300 rounded-b-full"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z M9 12l2 2 4-4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3 font-display">Shared Insight - Individual Edge</h3>
        <p class="text-charcoal-light text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          See how your performance stacks up against direct industry peers and neighbouring sectors — all anonymised. Benchmark against best practice and refine your strategy with confidence.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 group relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-100 hover:border-brand-200/60 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-brand-50">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-8 w-12 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-400 to-brand-300 rounded-b-full"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-charcoal mb-3 font-display">Simplified data and supplier governance</h3>
        <p class="text-charcoal-light text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          A single managed data interface replaces multiple point-to-point connections, reducing complexity and strengthening compliance in a regulated environment. You can now focus on performance and driving excellence in your business.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
